 and its agencies, on the mutually agreed terms and conditions;
 (l) promote financial inclusion in Pakistan;
 (m) develop financial market infrastructures;

 (n) participate in international councils and organizations, including
 multilateral, international financial institutions,

 (o) cooperate with domestic and foreign public entities, concerning matters
 related to its objectives and functions; and

 (p) carry out any ancillary activities incidental to the exercise of its
